{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迦道夫（Fes限定Ver.） 第5话 闪狼的意志",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "“贫民窟”事件数日之后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "迦道夫大人，您真的\\n要辞去特别顾问一职吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯，这是我和陛下商量后做出的决定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "虽说是为了拯救那里的居民，\\n但我的所作所为在这圣都的\\n规矩之下确实属于越权行为。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我必须为我的行为负责。\\n只是有些对不起为我介绍工作的陛下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "无论教会怎么说，\\n您的行为都值得我们尊敬。\\n您本不用受这么重的处罚……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我辞职的原因也不单是因为这个，\\n更是为了摆脱教会的束缚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "只要我在职一日，今后一举一动\\n就都会受到教会的干涉。\\n所以我还是以个人身份行动更为方便。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "您今后有什么打算啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这里把牺牲视作理所当然的做法\\n让我感到十分愤慨。所以我会慢慢\\n改变它，首先就从“贫民窟”开始。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "授人以鱼不如授人以渔。\\n单纯地施舍无法帮助他们摆脱贫困。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我要教会他们营生的手段，\\n从根本上改变他们的生存方式。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "真的能改变吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "当然，这需要“贫民窟”居民们的配合。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "据“贫民窟”的少女所说，\\n居民们最初看到席菈帮忙修补缺口时\\n都很讨厌她，认为她是来看笑话的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "但就算大家讨厌她，\\n她也坚持每天去“贫民窟”帮忙。\\n这才逐渐被居民们所接受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我也需要像她那样，\\n花时间通过交流与实际行动\\n来慢慢获取他们的信任。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "我很惭愧……\\n在迦道夫大人为了“贫民窟”而\\n行动的时候，我什么都没能做。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "因为我害怕会失去现在的地位……\\n可您又是如何办到的呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我也和你一样。\\n甚至现在也在害怕会失去至今为止\\n所积累的东西。但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "比起这些，我更怕让我的女儿失望。\\n仅此而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "让你久等了，席菈。\\n来，我们走吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "要做的事情很多，\\n你可要帮我啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "那之后的事你都知道了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我花了很长的时间与\\n“贫民窟”的居民建立了信赖关系。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "随后我建立了自治“贫民窟”的自卫团，\\n并为了以身作则而担任团长。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "多亏了席菈才有了现在的我。\\n是她让我变得清醒。\\n而且……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "一不小心说太久了……\\n再不睡的话要耽误明天的事了。\\n巡夜工作就交给我，你快去睡觉吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（我亲爱的朋友亚罗拉斯。\\n虽说我们的约定\\n在带他到精灵国之后就已经完成。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（但我打算陪尤蒂尔\\n走完他的旅程。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（因为如果没有你的建议，\\n我一定到现在都\\n还与席菈有着隔阂。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（请允许我用守护你的后代这种方式\\n来回报你的这份恩情……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}